--[[
[================]
Description: A-Life enhancements: NPC Personalities, Goals, and Dynamic PDA News Feed.
Written for Anomaly Together multiplayer.
Centralized message queue implemented to prevent message flooding and overlaps.
De-duplication system to prevent identical messages from firing simultaneously.
Intelligent smart terrain name parser to convert raw names (e.g., pri_a28_arch) into readable locations.
Dynamic NPC reaction to combat reports (Scavengers loot, Aggressors/Enforcers fight, Cowards flee).
Dynamic typing delay simulator for high-fidelity immersion.
Procedural sentence builder for infinite variation and complete immersion.
[================]
--]]

